 "data": "@startuml
title Blog System

actor 비회원 as NonMember
actor 사용자 as User
actor 관리자 as Admin

(게시글 조회) as ViewPosts
(공개된 게시글 조회) as ViewPublicPosts
(게시글 작성) as CreatePost
(게시글 수정) as EditPost
(게시글 삭제) as DeletePost
(좋아요) as LikePost
(댓글 작성) as WriteComment
(대댓글 작성) as WriteReply
(게시글 관리) as ManagePosts
(댓글 및 대댓글 관리) as ManageComments
(사용자 관리) as ManageUsers
(카테고리 관리) as ManageCategories
(태그 관리) as ManageTags
(통계 및 보고서) as GenerateReports

NonMember --> ViewPosts
ViewPosts --> ViewPublicPosts

User --> CreatePost
User --> EditPost
User --> DeletePost
User --> LikePost
User --> WriteComment
User --> WriteReply

Admin --> ManagePosts
Admin --> ManageComments
Admin --> ManageUsers
Admin --> ManageCategories
Admin --> ManageTags
Admin --> GenerateReports
